    public abstract class HtmlPhrasingElementNoTime<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>
extends HtmlCommonPhrasingElementNoTime<T>
    This abstract class defines phrasing elements but without the ability to create time elements as child elements This class adds the methods to create the child elements appropriate to phrasing elements

    simon
